oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: One of six farm ponds on the Evergreen Farms, owned by the Dudney Brothers; located near Gainesboro, Tenn., in Jackson County.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Built primarily to provide water for the livestock, the ponds also have been stocked with fish and provide relaxation through the fun of fishing as well as tasty food.
